title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

Dinesh D'Souza on covid madness, January 6th, lack of GOP leadership. CNN uses kids to push masks in schools. Where is the pushback against mask and vaccine mandates? America has become a country of sheep. Buck wishes Trump and Dr. Scott Atlas were still in charge. New Jersey Governor Murphy calls people who aren't vaccinated "knuckleheads".

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
